# Custom completions directory.
#
# Fish auto-loads completions from ~/.config/fish/completions/<command>.fish.
# Place one completion file per command here.
#
# Example: meowctl completions would live in meowctl.fish
#   complete -c meowctl -n '__fish_use_subcommand' -a 'apply' -d 'Apply configuration'
#
# For complex completions, study /usr/share/fish/completions/ as templates.
